---
title: Indian-Style Shrimp Curry with Rice, Bell Pepper, Onion & Cilantro
description: Curries just have a special way of warming your heart and your belly, and this Indian-style version is a case in point! Chicken thighs are cooked in earthy garam masala and creamy yogurt, then tossed with sautéed bell pepper, onion, garlic, and a deeply flavored curry sauce. Everything’s served over a bed of basmati, then sprinkled with cilantro and sliced chili pepper. Not so sure about the heat? Feel free to skip it altogether or slowly add it to your taste—just keep calm and curry on!
